{"word":"ἰατήρ","slug":"ἰατήρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰατήρ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <a href='S:ἰατρός'><el>ἰατρός</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>\n<p/><i>doctor, healer</i>, <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἰ. κακῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}